<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background-color: #3b82f6;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Snack25 초대 메일</h2>
      <p><strong>{{name}}</strong> 님, Snack25에 초대되었습니다.</p>
      <p>권한: <strong>{{translatedRole}}</strong></p>
      <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="button">가입하러 가기</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
